// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <case> => Statement
//  <case>* => List<Statement>
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <program> => Program
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 11: <type> ::= `int
// 12: <type> ::= `boolean
// 13: <type> ::= `void
// 14: <type> ::= `null
// 15: <type> ::= ID
// 16: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 17: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 18: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 19: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 20: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 21: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 22: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 23: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 24: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; <exp> `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 26: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 27: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 28: <assign> ::= ID `++
// 29: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 30: <stmt> ::= `;
// 31: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ <case>* `}
// 32: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ `}
// 33: <case> ::= `case <exp> `;
// 34: <exp> ::= <exp5>
// 35: <exp5> ::= <exp4>
// 36: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 37: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 38: <exp2> ::= <exp1>
// 39: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `< <exp4>
// 40: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `<= <exp4>
// 41: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `> <exp4>
// 42: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 43: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `- <exp3>
// 44: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 45: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 46: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 47: <exp2> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 48: <exp2> ::= `+ <exp1>
// 49: <exp2> ::= `- <exp1>
// 50: <exp2> ::= `! <exp1>
// 51: <exp1> ::= ID
// 52: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 53: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 54: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 55: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 56: <exp1> ::= `this
// 57: <exp1> ::= `true
// 58: <exp1> ::= `false
// 59: <exp1> ::= `null
// 60: <exp1> ::= `new ID `( `)
// 61: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 62: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 63: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 64: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 65: any ::= {0..127}
// 66: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 67: ws ::= " "
// 68: ws ::= {10}
// 69: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 70: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 71: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 72: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 73: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 74: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 75: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 76: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 77: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 78: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 79: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 80: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 81: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 82: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 83: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 84: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 85: `for ::= "#" "f" "o" ws*
// 86: `for ::= "#" "f" "o"
// 87: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 88: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 89: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 90: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 91: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 92: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 93: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 94: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 95: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 96: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 97: `new ::= "#" "n" "e" ws*
// 98: `new ::= "#" "n" "e"
// 99: `case ::= "#" "c" "e" ws*
// 100: `case ::= "#" "c" "e"
// 101: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 102: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 103: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w" ws*
// 104: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w"
// 105: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 106: `! ::= "!"
// 107: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 108: `% ::= "%"
// 109: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 110: `* ::= "*"
// 111: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 112: `( ::= "("
// 113: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 114: `) ::= ")"
// 115: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 116: `{ ::= "{"
// 117: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 118: `} ::= "}"
// 119: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 120: `- ::= "-"
// 121: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 122: `+ ::= "+"
// 123: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 124: `= ::= "="
// 125: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 126: `[ ::= "["
// 127: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 128: `] ::= "]"
// 129: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 130: `< ::= "<"
// 131: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 132: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 133: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 134: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 135: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 136: `; ::= ";"
// 137: `++ ::= "@" "+" ws*
// 138: `++ ::= "@" "+"
// 139: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 140: `/ ::= "/"
// 141: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 142: ID ::= letter128
// 143: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 144: ID ::= letter $$0
// 145: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 146: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1
// 147: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 148: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 149: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 150: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 151: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 152: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 153: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 154: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 155: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 156: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 157: idChar ::= letter
// 158: idChar ::= digit
// 159: idChar ::= "_"
// 160: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 161: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 162: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 163: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 164: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 165: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 166: digit* ::= digit
// 167: any* ::= any* any
// 168: any* ::= any
// 169: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 170: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 171: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 172: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 173: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 174: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 175: <case>* ::= <case>* <case>
// 176: <case>* ::= <case>
// 177: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 178: idChar* ::= idChar
// 179: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 180: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 181: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 182: ws* ::= ws
// 183: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 184: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 185: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 186: $$1 ::= digit128
// 187: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 188: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 189: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 190: $$3 ::= any128

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 59
        "#" => shift: 125
        ws => shift: 115
        <program> => shift: 199
        `class => shift: 434
        <start> => shift: 459
        ws* => shift: 255
        {10} => shift: 28
        " " => shift: 79
        <class decl> => shift: 448

**** STATE 4 ****
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null !<empty bracket pair> <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `%

**** STATE 5 ****
    `} ::= "}" ws* <!!`else%> // `else
    -----------------------

**** STATE 6 ****
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" !<empty bracket pair> [ws*] <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `%
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `)
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `*
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `+
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `-
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `/
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `;
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `<

    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // <empty bracket pair>
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // ID
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `%
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `)
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `*
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `+
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `++
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `-
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `/
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `;
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `<
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `<=
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `=
    ID ::= letter <%> idChar* $$0 // `>

**** STATE 115 ****

    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // $

**** STATE 396 ****
    ws* ::= ws* ws !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // ID
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `)
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `*
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `+
    ws* ::= ws* ws <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `++
